{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"교차축","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Glossary/Cross_Axis","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Flexbox\">플렉스박스</a>에서, <strong>교차축</strong>이란 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Main_Axis\">주축</a>에 수직하는 축으로, <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-direction\"><code>flex-direction</code></a>이 <code>row</code> 또는 <code>row-reverse</code> 인 경우 교차축은 열 방향을 따라갑니다.</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15710/Basics3.png\" alt=\"The cross axis runs down the column\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>주축이 <code>column</code> 또는 <code>column-reverse</code>인 경우 교차축은 행 방향을 따라갑니다.</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"https://mdn.mozillademos.org/files/15711/Basics4.png\" alt=\"The cross axis runs along the row.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>아이템을 교차축에 대해 정렬할 땐 플렉스 컨테이너의 <code>align-items</code> 속성 또는 각각 아이템의<code>align-self</code> 속성을 사용합니다. 플렉스 컨테이너가 콘텐츠 여러 줄을 가졌고, 교차축에 남는 공간이 있다면 <code>align-content</code> 속성을 통해 열 간격을 조절할 수 있습니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"더_알아보기","title":"더 알아보기","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"속성_참고서","title":"속성 참고서","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/align-content\"><code>align-content</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-items\"><code>align-items</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/align-self\"><code>align-self</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-wrap\"><code>flex-wrap</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-direction\"><code>flex-direction</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex\"><code>flex</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-basis\"><code>flex-basis</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-flow\"><code>flex-flow</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-grow\"><code>flex-grow</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/flex-shrink\"><code>flex-shrink</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/justify-content\"><code>justify-content</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/order\"><code>order</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"더_읽어보기","title":"더 읽어보기","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Flexbox\">Basic Concepts of Flexbox</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Aligning_Items_in_a_Flex_Container\">Aligning items in a flex container</a></em></li>\n  <li>CSS Flexbox Guide: <em><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout/Mastering_Wrapping_of_Flex_Items\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Mastering wrapping of flex items (en-US)</a></em>\n    <ul>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Flex\">Flex <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Flex_Container\">Flex Container</a></li>\n      <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Glossary/Flex_Item\">Flex Item</a></li>\n      <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid\">Grid <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"더 알아보기","id":"더_알아보기"}],"summary":"플렉스박스에서, 교차축이란 주축에 수직하는 축으로, flex-direction이 row 또는 row-reverse 인 경우 교차축은 열 방향을 따라갑니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Cross Axis","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Ax